        Social Media Marketing for Brisbane Property Listings: When Paid Facebook and Instagram Campaigns Pay Off
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Paid social has become a meaningful layer in Brisbane property marketing, but only for some properties. Understanding when a paid Facebook or Instagram campaign pulls its weight, and when it is a distraction, matters before agreeing the marketing budget.
      </p>
